The machine learning portion of our project.

1) Create a virtual environment: python3 -m venv venv
2) Go inside the virtual environment: source /venv/bin/activate
3) Install the required dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt
4) Run the pipeline: python3 run_pipeline --input parquet_data.parquet [--date_frac 0.3]
5) Generate a human-readable report: python3 generate_report.py --input signals.parquet --output report.txt

This assumes you already have a parquet of all the data you wish to train off of.
